OL,3,CTories to amend Equality Act to make
OL,4,C'biological sex' protected
OL,5,Ccharacteristic
OL,7,FThe Conservatives have pledged to
OL,8,Fchange the Equality Act to define the
OL,9,Fprotected characteristic of sex as
OL,10,F"biological sex".
OL,12,FThey claim the change will make it
OL,13,Fsimpler for service providers for
OL,14,Fwomen and girls, such as those running
OL,15,Fsessions for domestic abuse victims,
OL,16,Fto prevent biological males from
OL,17,Ftaking part.
