OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said: "The
OL,8,Fsafety of women and girls is too
OL,9,Fimportant to allow the current
OL,10,Fconfusion around definitions of sex
OL,11,Fand gender to persist.
OL,13,F"The Conservatives believe that making
OL,14,Fthis change in law will enhance
OL,15,Fprotections in a way that respects the
OL,16,Fprivacy and dignity of everyone in
OL,17,Fsociety.
