OL,7,F"We are taking an evidence-led
OL,8,Fapproach to this issue so we can
OL,9,Fcontinue to build a secure future for
OL,10,Feveryone across the whole country."
OL,12,FLast year Ms Badenoch wrote to the
OL,13,FEquality and Human Rights Commission
OL,14,F(EHRC) seeking further guidance on the
OL,15,Fissue.
OL,17,FShe said public bodies are acting out
OL,18,Fof "fear of being accused of
OL,19,Ftransphobia".
