OL,7,FThe minister said: "Whether it is
OL,8,Frapists being housed in women's
OL,9,Fprisons, or instances of men playing
OL,10,Fin women's sports where they have an
OL,11,Funfair advantage, it is clear that
OL,12,Fpublic authorities and regulatory
OL,13,Fbodies are confused about what the law
OL,14,Fsays on sex and gender and when to act
OL,15,F` often for fear of being accused of
OL,16,Ftransphobia, or not being inclusive.
OL,26,@oD@TOU
