OL,7,FThe women and equalities minister also
OL,8,Fattacked "activist organisations" such
OL,9,Fas Stonewall for exploiting loopholes
OL,10,Fin the law "for their own agenda".
OL,12,FShe wrote: "Clarification is required.
OL,13,FNot just to protect the privacy and
OL,14,Fdignity of women and girls, but also
OL,15,F... transpeople who were going about
OL,16,Ftheir lives in peace, until predators
OL,17,Fstarted exploiting loopholes in the
OL,18,Flaw by calling themselves trans with
OL,19,Fno evidence beyond their self-
OL,20,Fidentification."
