OL,7,FIn her article Ms Badenoch also
OL,8,Frevealed that a future Tory government
OL,9,Fwould legislate to strip the Scottish
OL,10,FParliament of its powers to legislate
OL,11,Fon issues surrounding gender
OL,12,Frecognition.
OL,14,FThe Gender Recognition Bill was passed
OL,15,Fin the Scottish Parliament in 2022 and
OL,16,Fwould have made it easier for
OL,17,Ftransgender people in Scotland to get
OL,18,Fgender recognition certificates.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
