OL,7,FMs Badenoch criticised the Labour
OL,8,Fleader, writing: "There are numerous
OL,9,Fexamples of Keir Starmer going round
OL,10,Fin circles on this issue.
OL,12,F"And many more of mostly Labour
OL,13,Fpoliticians smearing those with
OL,14,Fconcerns as 'transphobic' or 'far-
OL,15,Fright', dismissing the issue as mere
OL,16,F'culture wars'.
OL,26,@pD@ROUtD@AOU
