OL,7,F"They then bizarrely claim that the
OL,8,Fgovernment should stick to talking
OL,9,Fabout the economy and the NHS, as if
OL,10,Fwe should not be capable of solving
OL,11,Fmultiple things at once."
OL,13,FShe added: "A future Conservative
OL,14,Fgovernment will take bold action and
OL,15,Fintroduce primary legislation to
OL,16,Fclarify that the protected
OL,17,Fcharacteristic of sex in the Equality
OL,18,FAct means biological sex.
